<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<body>
    <h2 id="title">Self Care Quiz</h2>
    <div>
        <form id="quiz" name="quiz">
            <hr />
            <p><strong>What sounds better to you right now?</strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q1" value="1" /> A nap <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q1" value="2" /> Venting my frustrations <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q1" value="3" /> Something to get my heartrate going <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q1" value="4" /> A minute to myself <br />

            <hr />
            <p><strong>What do you typically do when you are stressed?</strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q2" value="4" /> Make as much work for myself as possible <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q2" value="2" /> Bottle it up and try to ignore it <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q2" value="1" /> Eat all the junk food I can <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q2" value="3" /> Find an excuse to stay on my feet and not sit down and think about it <br />

            <hr />
            <p><strong>You arrive at work and you have a pile of new tasks to do. Oh great. What is your reaction?</strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q3" value="2" /> Smile and pretend like you aren't freaking out inside <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q3" value="1" /> The sight of this literally makes me feel more unmotivated <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q3" value="4" /> No problem! Just add it to the millions of other things on my plate <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q3" value="3" /> I wish I was outdoors or doing anything other than this <br />

            <hr />

            <p><strong>Where would you like to be right now?</strong></p>
            <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q4" value="3" /> A park<br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q4" value="1" /> My room <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q4" value="4" /> Working <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q4" value="2" /> With a friend or family member <br />

            <hr />

            <p><strong>What kind of music do you listen to?</strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q5" value="4" /> I'm more of a podcast person<br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q5" value="1" /> Slow, sad songs <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q5" value="2" /> Aggressive<br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q5" value="3" /> Upbeat<br />

            <hr />
            <p><strong>Which fits you better?</strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q6" value="1" /> Low energy <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q6" value="3" /> Pent up energy <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q6" value="4" /> Busy body <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q6" value="2" /> Pent up emotions <br />

            <hr />
            <p><strong>When talking to people, what fits you better? </strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q7" value="2" /> I love talking to people <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q7" value="3" /> I use lots of gestures when I speak<br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q7" value="1" /> More on the shy side <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q7" value="4" /> I'm a good listener <br />

            <hr />
            <p><strong>You come home from a long day. What makes you feel better? </strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q8" value="3" /> A clean house <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q8" value="4" /> Extra time to relax <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q8" value="1" /> Eating comfort food <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q8" value="2" /> Talking to my friends/family <br />

            <hr />
            <p><strong>How active are you?</strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q9" value="1" /> Not at all <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q9" value="3" /> Super active<br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q9" value="2" /> Somewhat <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q9" value="4" /> Super active but not because I want to be <br />

            <hr />
            <p><strong>What is an ideal gift for you?</strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q10" value="2" /> A stress ball <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q10" value="4" /> A new book <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q10" value="1" /> Something to make me feel good about myself, like a new outfit<br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q10" value="3" /> New cleaning supplies <br />

            <hr />
            <p><strong>What scares you the most?</strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q11" value="2" /> Not being enough <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q11" value="3" /> Not experiencing enough <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q11" value="1" /> Not accomplishing things in my life <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q11" value="4" /> Not being able to be there for everyone<br />

            <hr />
            <p><strong>What are you more likely to experience when you're stressed?</strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q12" value="4" /> Headaches <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q12" value="2" /> Tension all over my body <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q12" value="3" /> Fatigue <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q12" value="1" /> Extreme lack of motivation <br />

            <hr />
            <p><strong>People would best describe me as...</strong></p>
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q13" value="3" /> Upbeat <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q13" value="4" /> Always on the go <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q13" value="1" /> Laid back <br />
            <input type="radio" id="multChoice" name="q13" value="2" /> Friendly <br />
            
            <br />

            <input type="button" value="All done!" onclick="check();" />

        </form>
    </div>
    <div id="result">

    </div>
</body>
</html>
